Package com.ninjaguild.dragoneggdrop.api

Enum PortalCrystal

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<PortalCrystal>
      • com.ninjaguild.dragoneggdrop.api.PortalCrystal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<PortalCrystal>
    public enum PortalCrystal
extends Enum<PortalCrystal>
    Represents all possible locations in which an end crystal may be spawned in regards to the End Portal found in The End.
    Author:
    Parker Hawke - 2008Choco
